\par   }{\f1\fs20\insrsid3097771\charrsid3097771 of unsuspecting guests past their unseeing eyes spoke louder than my coward's conscience.  }{\f1\fs20\insrsid7081140 
\par   }{\f1\fs20\insrsid3097771\charrsid3097771 The Circle of Stone and Shadow is here; its dark story has begun...}{\f1\fs20\insrsid3097771 
\par }{\f1\fs20\insrsid3097771\charrsid3097771 
