\par }{\f1\fs20\insrsid7081140   }{\f1\fs20\insrsid3097771\charrsid3097771 The Circle is kind}{\f1\fs20\insrsid3097771  to its new agents; the initial}{\f1\fs20\insrsid3097771\charrsid3097771  assignment, this test of skill, will be joyful and }{
\f1\fs20\insrsid7081140 
